{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 4037, "title": "fix: word-level diff ignores include_change_type_prefix", "body": "Fixes #3816\n\nWhen text filtering options are unchecked (e.g. \"Added lines\"), notification tokens like `{{ current_snapshot }}` contain diff markers like `(changed)` and `(into)` instead of clean text.\n\n**Root cause:** `customSequenceMatcher` passes `include_change_type_prefix` to line-level diff paths (delete, insert, multi-line replace) but not to `render_inline_word_diff` for single-line word-level replacements. The word-diff function always wrapped tokens in placemarkers regardless of this flag.\n\n**Before:** `render_inline_word_diff(\"73\", \"100\")` \u2192 `@changed_PLACEMARKER_OPEN73@changed_PLACEMARKER_CLOSED\\n@changed_into_PLACEMARKER_OPEN100@changed_into_PLACEMARKER_CLOSED`\n\n**After (with `include_change_type_prefix=False`):** `73\\n100`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Add `include_change_type_prefix` parameter to `render_inline_word_diff` (default `True`, backwards compatible)\n- Pass it through from `customSequenceMatcher` on the word-diff call path\n- Conditionally skip placemarker wrapping in both the whole-line-replaced and inline-changes branches\n- Add 3 regression tests\n\nAll 26 unit tests pass.", "baseRefName": "master", "baseRefOid": "77116f520361cedf4a568c6af74863b0c565892a", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "dgtlmoon/changedetection.io"}, "url": "https://github.com/dgtlmoon/changedetection.io/pull/4037", "createdAt": "2026-04-10T01:35:34Z", "mergedAt": "2026-04-10T09:46:55Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "dgtlmoon/changedetection.io"}, "sha": "77116f520361cedf4a568c6af74863b0c565892a"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/dgtlmoon/changedetection.io/pull/4037.diff", "number": 4037, "created_at": "2026-04-10T01:35:34Z", "merged_at": "2026-04-10T09:46:55Z", "resolved_issues": [3816]}
