{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 3940, "title": "fix(i18n): accept translated confirmation text when clearing snapshot history", "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- The clear history confirmation dialog displayed the translated word (e.g. `loschen` in German) but the backend only accepted the hardcoded English word `clear`, making it impossible to clear snapshots in non-English languages.\r\n- Use `gettext('clear')` to dynamically resolve the expected confirmation word at runtime, so all supported language translations are accepted.\r\n- Added test to verify German confirmation word is accepted and English still works.\r\n\r\nCloses #3865\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- `changedetectionio/blueprint/ui/__init__.py`: Replace hardcoded `'clear'` comparison with `gettext('clear')` for locale-aware matching\r\n- `changedetectionio/tests/test_i18n.py`: Add `test_clear_history_translated_confirmation` covering German and English confirmation\r\n\r\n## Test plan\r\n\r\n- [x] Set language to German, navigate to clear history, type `loschen` - should succeed\r\n- [x] Set language back to English, type `clear` - should still succeed\r\n- [x] Case-insensitive and whitespace-trimmed comparison for robustness", "baseRefName": "master", "baseRefOid": "b984426666a6f3ea9fa9645ea05992567a72427e", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "dgtlmoon/changedetection.io"}, "url": "https://github.com/dgtlmoon/changedetection.io/pull/3940", "createdAt": "2026-03-02T08:48:41Z", "mergedAt": "2026-03-02T09:44:42Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "dgtlmoon/changedetection.io"}, "sha": "b984426666a6f3ea9fa9645ea05992567a72427e"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/dgtlmoon/changedetection.io/pull/3940.diff", "number": 3940, "created_at": "2026-03-02T08:48:41Z", "merged_at": "2026-03-02T09:44:42Z", "resolved_issues": [3865]}
